import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react';
import { motion } from 'framer-motion';
import './InfinityLogo.css';

function InfinityLogo({ size = 200, animated = true, showLabels = true }) {
  const [isHovered, setIsHovered] = useState(false);

  const pathVariants = {
    hidden: { pathLength: 0, opacity: 0 },
    visible: {
      pathLength: 1,
      opacity: 1,
      transition: { duration: 2, ease: "easeInOut" }
    }
  };

  const textVariants = {
    hidden: { opacity: 0 },
    visible: (i) => ({
      opacity: 1,
      transition: { delay: 1.5 + i * 0.1, duration: 0.5 }
    })
  };

  return (
    <motion.div 
      className="infinity-logo-container"
      onMouseEnter={() => setIsHovered(true)}
      onMouseLeave={() => setIsHovered(false)}
    >
      <svg 
        width={size} 
        height={size * 0.5} 
        viewBox="0 0 500 250" 
        fill="none" 
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      >
        {/* Left Circle (DEV) - Filled */}
        <motion.circle
          cx="125"
          cy="125"
          r="80"
          fill="var(--accent-primary)"
          variants={animated ? pathVariants : {}}
          initial="hidden"
          animate="visible"
        />
        
        {/* Right Circle (OPS) - Filled */}
        <motion.circle
          cx="375"
          cy="125"
          r="80"
          fill="var(--accent-primary)"
          variants={animated ? pathVariants : {}}
          initial="hidden"
          animate="visible"
        />
        
        {/* Center white circles for text */}
        <circle cx="125" cy="125" r="55" fill="var(--bg-primary)" />
        <circle cx="375" cy="125" r="55" fill="var(--bg-primary)" />
        
        {/* DEV Text */}
        <motion.text
          x="125"
          y="140"
          fontSize="36"
          fontWeight="900"
          fill="var(--text-primary)"
          textAnchor="middle"
          custom={0}
          variants={animated ? textVariants : {}}
          initial="hidden"
          animate="visible"
        >
          DEV
        </motion.text>
        
        {/* OPS Text */}
        <motion.text
          x="375"
          y="140"
          fontSize="36"
          fontWeight="900"
          fill="var(--text-primary)"
          textAnchor="middle"
          custom={1}
          variants={animated ? textVariants : {}}
          initial="hidden"
          animate="visible"
        >
          OPS
        </motion.text>
        
        {showLabels && (
          <>
            {/* Top Left Arrow */}
            <motion.path
              d="M 80,50 L 60,40 L 70,30"
              stroke="var(--bg-primary)"
              strokeWidth="4"
              fill="none"
              strokeLinecap="round"
              strokeLinejoin="round"
              custom={2}
              variants={animated ? textVariants : {}}
              initial="hidden"
              animate="visible"
            />
            
            {/* Bottom Left Arrow */}
            <motion.path
              d="M 170,200 L 190,210 L 180,220"
              stroke="var(--bg-primary)"
              strokeWidth="4"
              fill="none"
              strokeLinecap="round"
              strokeLinejoin="round"
              custom={3}
              variants={animated ? textVariants : {}}
              initial="hidden"
              animate="visible"
            />
            
            {/* Top Right Arrow */}
            <motion.path
              d="M 330,50 L 310,40 L 320,30"
              stroke="var(--bg-primary)"
              strokeWidth="4"
              fill="none"
              strokeLinecap="round"
              strokeLinejoin="round"
              custom={4}
              variants={animated ? textVariants : {}}
              initial="hidden"
              animate="visible"
            />
            
            {/* Bottom Right Arrow */}
            <motion.path
              d="M 420,200 L 440,210 L 430,220"
              stroke="var(--bg-primary)"
              strokeWidth="4"
              fill="none"
              strokeLinecap="round"
              strokeLinejoin="round"
              custom={5}
              variants={animated ? textVariants : {}}
              initial="hidden"
              animate="visible"
            />
            
            {/* Center Arrows */}
            <motion.path
              d="M 230,125 L 250,125 M 245,120 L 250,125 L 245,130"
              stroke="var(--text-secondary)"
              strokeWidth="3"
              fill="none"
              strokeLinecap="round"
              strokeLinejoin="round"
              custom={6}
              variants={animated ? textVariants : {}}
              initial="hidden"
              animate="visible"
            />
            
            <motion.path
              d="M 270,125 L 250,125 M 255,120 L 250,125 L 255,130"
              stroke="var(--text-secondary)"
              strokeWidth="3"
              fill="none"
              strokeLinecap="round"
              strokeLinejoin="round"
              custom={7}
              variants={animated ? textVariants : {}}
              initial="hidden"
              animate="visible"
            />
            
            {/* Labels */}
            <motion.text
              x="125"
              y="25"
              fontSize="12"
              fontWeight="600"
              fill="var(--text-secondary)"
              textAnchor="middle"
              custom={8}
              variants={animated ? textVariants : {}}
              initial="hidden"
              animate="visible"
            >
              Plan / Code
            </motion.text>
            
            <motion.text
              x="125"
              y="240"
              fontSize="12"
              fontWeight="600"
              fill="var(--text-secondary)"
              textAnchor="middle"
              custom={9}
              variants={animated ? textVariants : {}}
              initial="hidden"
              animate="visible"
            >
              Build / Integrate
            </motion.text>
            
            <motion.text
              x="375"
              y="25"
              fontSize="12"
              fontWeight="600"
              fill="var(--text-secondary)"
              textAnchor="middle"
              custom={10}
              variants={animated ? textVariants : {}}
              initial="hidden"
              animate="visible"
            >
              Test / Release
            </motion.text>
            
            <motion.text
              x="375"
              y="240"
              fontSize="12"
              fontWeight="600"
              fill="var(--text-secondary)"
              textAnchor="middle"
              custom={11}
              variants={animated ? textVariants : {}}
              initial="hidden"
              animate="visible"
            >
              Deploy / Monitor
            </motion.text>
          </>
        )}
      </svg>
    </motion.div>
  );
}

export default InfinityLogo;
